name: Olive Tree
description: Olive tree is a traditional Mediterranean tree valued for its olives and olive oil.

name: Mulberry Tree
description: Mulberry tree produces sweet edible berries and is popular for shade and fruit.

name: Jasmine
description: Jasmine is a fragrant flower known for its sweet scent, often used in perfumes and teas.

name: Anemone
description: Anemone is a delicate flower with vibrant colors, symbolizing protection and anticipation.

name: Carob Tree
description: Carob tree is a hardy evergreen shrub or tree known for its edible pods and sweet carob powder.

name: Spinach
description: Spinach is a nutritious leafy green vegetable rich in iron, vitamins, and antioxidants.

name: Chamomile
description: Chamomile is a fragrant herb used mainly for herbal teas known for its calming effects.

name: Purslane
description: Purslane is a succulent plant often used in salads, rich in omega-3 fatty acids.

name: Fig Tree
description: Fig tree is known for its sweet fruit and is widely cultivated in warm climates.

name: Poppy
description: Poppy is a bright flower symbolizing remembrance and consolation, often used ornamentally.

name: Alo Vera
description: Aloe Vera is a succulent plant used for its soothing gel with skin healing properties.

name: Mallow
description: Mallow is a flowering plant known for its medicinal and culinary uses.

name: Dandelion
description: Dandelion is a resilient plant with bright yellow flowers, used in herbal remedies.

name: Mint
description: Mint is a fragrant herb used for culinary and medicinal purposes, known for its fresh aroma.

name: Basil
description: Basil is a flavorful herb commonly used in cooking, especially in Mediterranean cuisine.

name: Parsley
description: Parsley is a versatile herb often used as garnish and for its fresh taste in dishes.

name: Sage
description: Sage is a fragrant herb used in cooking and traditional medicine.

name: Thyme
description: Thyme is a culinary herb known for its earthy flavor and medicinal properties.

name: Lavender
description: Lavender is a fragrant flowering plant used in aromatherapy and perfumes.

name: Marjoram
description: Marjoram is an aromatic herb used to flavor soups, stews, and sauces.

name: Oregano
description: Oregano is a popular culinary herb with a robust flavor, commonly used in Mediterranean dishes.

name: Tarragon
description: Tarragon is an aromatic herb with a slight licorice flavor used in cooking.

name: Dill
description: Dill is an herb used for flavoring pickles and various dishes.

name: Fennel
description: Fennel is a flavorful herb with a sweet, anise-like taste.

name: Zaater
description: Zaater is a Middle Eastern herb blend often used as a seasoning or condiment.

name: Rosemary
description: Rosemary is a fragrant evergreen herb used in cooking and for medicinal purposes.

name: Snapdragon
description: Snapdragon is a colorful flowering plant often used in gardens for decoration.

name: Tulip
description: Tulip is a popular spring-blooming flower with bright, cup-shaped petals.

name: Anise
description: Anise is a herb known for its licorice-like flavor, used in cooking and herbal remedies.
